56857.en:
<voice 00070_00056857><start_lip_sync n02233 _normal m00001>Who the hell are ya!? I ain't see your face around
here before!!<stop_lip_animation n02233 CLOSE_MOUTH>
56857.ja:
<voice 00070_00056857><start_lip_sync n02233 _normal m00001>「なんだ　てめえ！？
　ここいらじゃ　見ねえ顔だな！！<stop_lip_animation n02233 CLOSE_MOUTH>
56857.ko:
<voice 00070_00056857><start_lip_sync n02233 _normal m00001>: 누구냐, 넌!?
　이 근방에선 못 보던 얼굴이군!!<stop_lip_animation n02233 CLOSE_MOUTH>
56857.zh-Hans:
<voice 00070_00056857><start_lip_sync n02233 _normal m00001>你这家伙是谁啊？
你不是这里的人吧！<stop_lip_animation n02233 CLOSE_MOUTH>
56857.zh-Hant:
<voice 00070_00056857><start_lip_sync n02233 _normal m00001>你誰啊！？
沒看過的傢伙！！<stop_lip_animation n02233 CLOSE_MOUTH>

56858.en:
<voice 00160_00056858><start_lip_sync n02233 _normal m00001>To think ya've got the nerve coming to a place like
this; you friends with that damned debt collector?
I don't know about some debtor, got it!<stop_lip_animation n02233 CLOSE_MOUTH>
56858.ja:
<voice 00160_00056858><start_lip_sync n02233 _normal m00001>「こんな所まで　来やがるなんて
　さては　てめえ　あの借金取りの仲間だな？
　代替わりしても　オレには　わかるぜ！<stop_lip_animation n02233 CLOSE_MOUTH>
56858.ko:
<voice 00160_00056858><start_lip_sync n02233 _normal m00001>: 이런 곳까지 찾아온 걸 보니
　그 빚쟁이의 동료로군?
　다른 사람을 보내도 난 못 속여!<stop_lip_animation n02233 CLOSE_MOUTH>
56858.zh-Hans:
<voice 00160_00056858><start_lip_sync n02233 _normal m00001>居然跑到这种地方来。
……你是那个追债人的同伙吧？
就算换了人我也知道！<stop_lip_animation n02233 CLOSE_MOUTH>
56858.zh-Hant:
<voice 00160_00056858><start_lip_sync n02233 _normal m00001>你來這種地方，
難不成是那個討債的同夥？
就算換了人我也能認出來！<stop_lip_animation n02233 CLOSE_MOUTH>

56859.en:
<voice 00220_00056859><start_lip_sync n02233 _normal m00001>However! No matter how many times you ask for their
whereabouts, it's futile!!<stop_lip_animation n02233 CLOSE_MOUTH>
56859.ja:
<voice 00220_00056859><start_lip_sync n02233 _normal m00001>「だが！　何度　アイツの居所を
　聞きにきても　無駄だ！！<stop_lip_animation n02233 CLOSE_MOUTH>
56859.ko:
<voice 00220_00056859><start_lip_sync n02233 _normal m00001>: 하지만! 아무리 그 녀석이
　있는 곳을 물어도 소용없어!!<stop_lip_animation n02233 CLOSE_MOUTH>
56859.zh-Hans:
<voice 00220_00056859><start_lip_sync n02233 _normal m00001>不过！问我几回都没用！
我不知道那家伙在哪里！<stop_lip_animation n02233 CLOSE_MOUTH>
56859.zh-Hant:
<voice 00220_00056859><start_lip_sync n02233 _normal m00001>不過！不管你問我幾次那傢伙住哪，
都是沒有用的！！<stop_lip_animation n02233 CLOSE_MOUTH>

56860.en:
<voice 00285_00056860><start_lip_sync n02233 _normal m00001><kyodai> hasn't came this whole time, and I've
got no way of contacting them!!<stop_lip_animation n02233 CLOSE_MOUTH>
56860.ja:
<voice 00285_00056860><start_lip_sync n02233 _normal m00001>「<kyodai>は　もう　ずーっと
　ここには　来ちゃいねえし
　連絡も　取り合ってねえんだからよっ！！<stop_lip_animation n02233 CLOSE_MOUTH>
56860.ko:
<voice 00285_00056860><start_lip_sync n02233 _normal m00001>: {kyodai}|hpp(은,는) 이곳에 안 온 지
　이미 한참이나 된 데다
　연락도 끊겼으니까!!<stop_lip_animation n02233 CLOSE_MOUTH>
56860.zh-Hans:
<voice 00285_00056860><start_lip_sync n02233 _normal m00001><kyodai>已经
很久没有来过这里了。
我们也没有联系了！<stop_lip_animation n02233 CLOSE_MOUTH>
56860.zh-Hant:
<voice 00285_00056860><start_lip_sync n02233 _normal m00001><kyodai>已經很久
沒來這裡了，
我們也沒聯絡！<stop_lip_animation n02233 CLOSE_MOUTH>

56862.en:
<voice 00380_00056862><start_lip_sync n02233 _normal m00001>...What? You playin' dumb. You... Are friends with
that debt collector aren'tcha?<yesno><close><stop_lip_animation n02233 CLOSE_MOUTH>
56862.ja:
<voice 00380_00056862><start_lip_sync n02233 _normal m00001>「……なんだあ？　とぼけた顔しやがって。
　お前……　あの借金取りの　仲間じゃねえのか？<yesno><close><stop_lip_animation n02233 CLOSE_MOUTH>
56862.ko:
<voice 00380_00056862><start_lip_sync n02233 _normal m00001>: ……뭐냐? 그 얼빠진 얼굴은.
　너…… 그 빚쟁이의 동료가 아닌 거냐?<yesno><close><stop_lip_animation n02233 CLOSE_MOUTH>
56862.zh-Hans:
<voice 00380_00056862><start_lip_sync n02233 _normal m00001>……怎么了？
你一脸不明白我在说什么的表情。
你……难道不是追债人的同伙？<yesno><close><stop_lip_animation n02233 CLOSE_MOUTH>
56862.zh-Hant:
<voice 00380_00056862><start_lip_sync n02233 _normal m00001>……什麼？你怎麼一副不知道的樣子。
你難道……不是討債的同夥？<yesno><close><stop_lip_animation n02233 CLOSE_MOUTH>

56863.en:
<voice 00430_00056863><start_lip_sync n02233 _normal m00001>Mmm... Is that so, not a debt collector, is ya.
Now that you say it, you don't got the face of one.<stop_lip_animation n02233 CLOSE_MOUTH>
56863.ja:
<voice 00430_00056863><start_lip_sync n02233 _normal m00001>「ふむ……。
　そうか　借金取りじゃなかったのか。
　言われてみれば　それっぽくない顔だな。<stop_lip_animation n02233 CLOSE_MOUTH>
56863.ko:
<voice 00430_00056863><start_lip_sync n02233 _normal m00001>: 흠…….
　그렇군, 빚쟁이가 아니었나.
　듣고 보니 빚쟁이같이 생기진 않았군.<stop_lip_animation n02233 CLOSE_MOUTH>
56863.zh-Hans:
<voice 00430_00056863><start_lip_sync n02233 _normal m00001>嗯……
原来你不是追债的。
这么一说，你看起来确实不像是来追债的。<stop_lip_animation n02233 CLOSE_MOUTH>
56863.zh-Hant:
<voice 00430_00056863><start_lip_sync n02233 _normal m00001>嗯……
原來你不是來討債的啊。
這麼一說你看起來也不像嘛。<stop_lip_animation n02233 CLOSE_MOUTH>

56864.en:
<voice 00460_00056864><start_lip_sync n02233 _normal m00001>...So, why'd you come to a place like this? Who the
hell are ya?<stop_lip_animation n02233 CLOSE_MOUTH>
56864.ja:
<voice 00460_00056864><start_lip_sync n02233 _normal m00001>「……で　こんな所まで　何しに来やがった？
　お前　いったい　何者だ？<stop_lip_animation n02233 CLOSE_MOUTH>
56864.ko:
<voice 00460_00056864><start_lip_sync n02233 _normal m00001>: ……그럼 이런 곳에는 무슨 일로 온 거냐?
　너 대체 뭐 하는 녀석이야?<stop_lip_animation n02233 CLOSE_MOUTH>
56864.zh-Hans:
<voice 00460_00056864><start_lip_sync n02233 _normal m00001>……那你到底来这里干什么？
你到底是什么人？<stop_lip_animation n02233 CLOSE_MOUTH>
56864.zh-Hant:
<voice 00460_00056864><start_lip_sync n02233 _normal m00001>……那你來這裡做什麼？
你到底是什麼人？<stop_lip_animation n02233 CLOSE_MOUTH>

56865.en:
<voice 00650_00056865><start_lip_sync n02233 _normal m00001>...Hoo, <pc>, are ya. Huh? <pc>...
Where have I heard that name...<stop_lip_animation n02233 CLOSE_MOUTH>
56865.ja:
<voice 00650_00056865><start_lip_sync n02233 _normal m00001>「……ほう　<pc>というのか。
　ん？　<pc>……
　どっかで聞いた　名前だな……。<stop_lip_animation n02233 CLOSE_MOUTH>
56865.ko:
<voice 00650_00056865><start_lip_sync n02233 _normal m00001>: ……오호, {pc}|hpp(이란,란) 말이지.
　응? <pc>……
　어디서 들어 본 이름인데…….<stop_lip_animation n02233 CLOSE_MOUTH>
56865.zh-Hans:
<voice 00650_00056865><start_lip_sync n02233 _normal m00001>……哦，你叫<pc>啊？
嗯？<pc>……
我好像在哪里听过这个名字……<stop_lip_animation n02233 CLOSE_MOUTH>
56865.zh-Hant:
<voice 00650_00056865><start_lip_sync n02233 _normal m00001>……你叫<pc>啊。
嗯？<pc>……
我好像在哪聽過這名字……<stop_lip_animation n02233 CLOSE_MOUTH>

98484.en:
<voice 00800_00098484><start_lip_sync n02233 _normal m00001>Anyways! Ya've got no business entering someone's
house! Understand!?<stop_lip_animation n02233 CLOSE_MOUTH>
98484.ja:
<voice 00800_00098484><start_lip_sync n02233 _normal m00001>「とにかく！　用もないのに人の家に
　あがり込むんじゃねえ！　わかったな！？<stop_lip_animation n02233 CLOSE_MOUTH>
98484.ko:
<voice 00800_00098484><start_lip_sync n02233 _normal m00001>: 아무튼! 용건도 없이 남의 집에
　함부로 들어오지 마라! 알겠느냐!?<stop_lip_animation n02233 CLOSE_MOUTH>
98484.zh-Hans:
<voice 00800_00098484><start_lip_sync n02233 _normal m00001>不管怎样！没什么事
就别随便闯进别人家里！明白没有？！<stop_lip_animation n02233 CLOSE_MOUTH>
98484.zh-Hant:
<voice 00800_00098484><start_lip_sync n02233 _normal m00001>總之！沒什麼事
就別隨便闖進別人家裡！聽到沒有！？<stop_lip_animation n02233 CLOSE_MOUTH>
